snippet.title: Segata Sanshiro - Pro Yakyuu Greatest Nine '98
snippet.description:
Relase date: 03/26/98

Pro Yakyuu Greatest Nine '98 is a Baseball Sim game, developed by NexTech and published by Sega, which was released in Japan in 1998.
